{"id": 1938, "name": "Texte de la commission sur la proposition de loi de M. Olivier Falorni relative \u00e0 la fin de vie (1100)., n\u00b0\u00a01364-A0", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/1364/AN/1938", "date": "2025-05-09", "status": "Rejet\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Lisette", "last_name": "Pollet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Anne", "last_name": "Sicard", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thibaut", "last_name": "Monnier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Eddy", "last_name": "Casterman", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ren\u00e9", "last_name": "Lioret", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Christophe", "last_name": "Bentz", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jo\u00eblle", "last_name": "M\u00e9lin", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Alexandre", "last_name": "Dufosset", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Marie-France", "last_name": "Lorho", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Herv\u00e9", "last_name": "de L\u00e9pinau", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Florence", "last_name": "Joubert", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Caroline", "last_name": "Colombier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "B\u00e9n\u00e9dicte", "last_name": "Auzanot", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Fouquart", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Frapp\u00e9", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Sophie", "last_name": "Blanc", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Sandrine", "last_name": "Dogor-Such", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Alexandre", "last_name": "Allegret-Pilot", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "Mich\u00e8le", "last_name": "Martinez", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jorys", "last_name": "Bovet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Catherine", "last_name": "Rimbert", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Rambaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jonathan", "last_name": "Gery", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric-Pierre", "last_name": "Vos", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Pierre", "last_name": "Meurin", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Th\u00e9o", "last_name": "Bernhardt", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Katiana", "last_name": "Levavasseur", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Limongi", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Frank", "last_name": "Giletti", "party": "Rassemblement National"}], "summary": "Le but de cette proposition de loi n\u2019est pas d\u2019encourager les souffrants au suicide lorsqu\u2019une solution efficace existe, mais de soulager les souffrances irr\u00e9ductibles.\nAinsi, cet amendement restreint le recours \u00e0 l\u2019euthanasie aux cas o\u00f9 les souffrances endur\u00e9es ne peuvent \u00eatre soulag\u00e9es par aucun traitement. En effet, la r\u00e9daction actuelle de l\u2019article\u00a04 permet \u00e0 la personne de recourir \u00e0 l\u2019euthanasie tout en ayant refus\u00e9 un traitement dont l\u2019efficacit\u00e9 est \u00e9prouv\u00e9e."}